songs.title: Northern Downpour (Snippet)
songs.album: CitizensFOB Mixtape: Welcome to the New Administration
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1:]
The ink is running toward the page, it’s chasing off the days
Look back at both feet and that winding knee
(Welcome To The New Administration, suckers!)
The ink is running toward the page
(Call me the hip-hop rockstar)
It’s chasing off the days
Look back at both feet and that winding knee
I missed your skin when you were east
You clicked your heels and wished for me

Through playful lips made of yarn, that fragile Capricorn
Unraveled words like moths upon old scarves
I know the world’s a broken bone
But melt your headaches, call it home

[Chorus 1:]
Hey moon, please forget to fall down
Hey moon, don’t you go down
Sugarcane in the easy morning
Weather vanes my one and lonely

[Bridge:]
Sugarcane in the easy morning
Weather vanes my one and lonely

The new administration, the new administration
You know what this is
The new administration
It's the new administration
The new administration
Fall Out Boy mixtape
The new administration
Are we going too slow for you?
The new administration
How about we speed it up?
The new administration, the new administration, the new administration, the new administration
Get familiar! New Fall Out Boy album dropping November 4th!
The new administration, the new administration
Friendsorenemies.com, clintonsparks.com, [? 1:45] suckers

Here I am
The new administration
H-h-here I am, here
The new administration
Here, here I am, here
The new administration
Here, here I am, here I, here I
The new administration
Here I am, here
The new administration
Y'all ready!
Here I, here I, here I
